ent-AU14WeaponRifleprodigyrifleAR = MCS-X Pulse Rifle
    .desc = The Modular Combat System Mark X Pulse Rifle, or MCS-X Pulse Rifle for short, is the standard weapon used by the prodigy security forces employed by Prodigy Corporation. The weapon has a bullpup design, intended for use in cramped urban environments. The MCS-X features a digital ammunition counter, and is capable of holding ninety-five rounds.
